                            


                                        How To Create Your First Flutter Application
                                        --------------------------------------------
					--------------------------------------------

1- Select the operating system on which you are installing Flutter:

		Linux:

			Download the following installation bundle to get the latest stable release of the Flutter SDK:


			Installation Link:-	https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install/linux


2- Extract the file in the desired location, for example:

		
    (1)-Open Terminal

     (2)-Write the following Command where you want to extract that Flutter tar File:

              tar xf ~/Downloads/flutter_linux_v1.5.4-hotfix.2-stable.tar.xz



3-  Add the flutter tool to your path:

		Where you want to extract and Create your First Flutter App inside that Folder:

			export PATH="$PATH:'pwd'/flutter/bin"


		pwd:- This the path of that flutter directory where you have extracted your flutter tar file.



4- Run the following command to see if there are any dependencies you need to install to complete the setup

		
		flutter doctor


5- After that in the above folder run this Command for creation of Flutter Application.

		1- flutter create my_flutter_application

		2- cd my_flutter_application
		
		3- flutter run 
